alarmConfigEntry.name: alarmConfigEntry
alarmConfigEntry.description: An entry in the alarm configuration table.

alarmConfigBitRateThreshold.name: alarmConfigBitRateThreshold
alarmConfigBitRateThreshold.description: This field describes the enable status of the Bit Rate Threshold Alarm. If this field is true (1) then the Bit Rate Threshold alarm is enabled. If this field is false (2) then the Bit Rate Threshold Alarm is disabled.

alarmConfigBitRateThresholdValue.name: alarmConfigBitRateThresholdValue
alarmConfigBitRateThresholdValue.description: This field indicates the Bit Rate Threshold Value which will generate an alarm if the Bit Rate Threshold Alarm is enabled and the Bit Rate of this ifIndex drops below this value.

alarmConfigBitRateThresholdHoldtime.name: alarmConfigBitRateThresholdHoldtime
alarmConfigBitRateThresholdHoldtime.description: This field indicates the Bit Rate Threshold Holdtime in seconds for which the Bit Rate of the ifIndex must remain below the Bit Rate Threshold Value before an alarm will be generated if the Bit Rate Threshold Alarm is enabled.

alarmConfigStatusTrap.name: alarmConfigStatusTrap
alarmConfigStatusTrap.description: This field describes the enable status of the Status Trap Alarm. If this field is true (1) then the Status Trap alarm is enabled. If this field is false (2) then the Status Trap Alarm is disabled.

alarmConfigAdminUp.name: alarmConfigAdminUp
alarmConfigAdminUp.description: This field describes the enable status of the Admin Up Alarm. If this field is true (1) then the Admin Up alarm is enabled. If this field is false (2) then the Admin Up Alarm is disabled.

alarmConfigAlarmSeverity.name: alarmConfigAlarmSeverity
alarmConfigAlarmSeverity.description: This object is used to override Trap, Central Alarm Manager and CLI 'LineAlarm' severity levels for the specified interface.

alarmConfigRowStatus.name: alarmConfigRowStatus
alarmConfigRowStatus.description: This object is used to create, delete or modify a row in this table.

zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdTrap.name: zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdTrap
zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdTrap.description: This Trap is generated when this ifIndex bandwidth drops below the alarmConfigBitRateThresholdValue for the time specified in alarmConfigBitRateThesholdHoldtime.

zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdClearTrap.name: zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdClearTrap
zhoneAlarmConfigThresholdClearTrap.description: This trap is generated when this ifIndex bandwidth goes above the alarmConfigBitRateThresholdValue for the time specified in alarmConfigBitRateThresholdHoldtime.
